text: Rudolf Vilim (born June 15, 1913) is a Swiss canoeist who competed in the 1936 Summer Olympics. In 1936 he and his partner Werner Klingelfuss finished fifth in the K-2 1000 metres competition. ==References== *Sports-reference.com profile Category:1913 births Category:Canoeists at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic canoeists of Switzerland Category:Possibly living people Category:Swiss male canoeists
